an style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="10" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.78pt; padding-left:6.67pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> Any other relevant issues</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">10.1</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">I believe that in my first year in office I have made a real difference to reducing crime and addressing Community Safety issues in Avon and Somerset by focussing on the key roles highlighted above. There remains much more to be done and I am comfortable that I will be judged on the success of these various initiatives at the end of my 3 and a half year term. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="11" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.78pt; padding-left:6.67pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> Declaration of interests</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; 